{"Name":"CT FoodNEX","ShortName":"CT FoodNEX","Description":"CT FoodNEX is a freehold, purpose-built food factory in Mandai. Featuring a fully ramped-up design for direct vehicle access, high ceilings with mezzanine options, and integrated food-grade infrastructure, it ensures both efficiency and hygiene for businesses. Strategically located near major expressways and the future Sungei Kadut Eco-District, CT FoodNEX offers immense long-term value.","StartUrl":"/","Display":"standalone","BackgroundColor":"#ffffff","ThemeColor":"#041e42","Orientation":"portrait","Icons":[{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/18f710df-c309-4153-bf3e-a7c9fae2bda8","Sizes":"192x192","Type":"image/png"},{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/18f710df-c309-4153-bf3e-a7c9fae2bda8","Sizes":"512x512","Type":"image/png"}]}